			</div>
		</div>
	</Section>
	<Section padding="none" />
	<Section padding="top">
		<Row
			><Col span="12" align="center" classes="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-pretty"><strong>REGIONE SOCIALE</strong></h2>
				<h4>
					RETE ITALIANA DELL3 ALLIEV3 DELLE SCUOLE E DEGLI ISTITUTI DI STUDI SUPERIORI
					UNIVERSITARI - APS
				</h4>
			</Col></Row
		>
	</Section>
	<Section padding="both">
		<Row>
			<Col span="12" align="center" classes="mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="text-pretty"><strong>CODICE FISCALE</strong></h2>
			</Col>
			</Row>
			<Row>
				<Col span="12" align="center" classes="mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
